The,Rooftop,CMS,API,facilitates,the,construction,of,apps,that,are,responsive,to,cross,platform,and,multi,language,content,management,environments,It,is,essentially,a,WordPress,solution,that,developers,can,use,to,implement,CMS,applications,in,any,language,It,makes,it,easier,for,non,PHP,developers,to,integrate,WordPress,functionalities,in,their,CMSs,The,API,s,provider,s,ability,to,host,content,spares,developers,the,need,to,generate,WordPress,themes,The,RESTful,API,sends,requests,in,JSON,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,and,Webhooks,formats